{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01ATaRqbUWaQ9sGQGhCUELhA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The pods are up and running, but the DNS for `es-0.es-headless`, `es-1.es-headless`, and `es-2.es-headless` cannot resolve. This means the headless service DNS entries are not resolving. \n\nThis is a common issue: the headless service DNS entry for each pod (`es-N.es-headless.elasticsearch.svc.cluster.local`) only resolves when the pod is \"Ready\". Since the pods are not ready, the DNS doesn't resolve. The pods become Ready only after the readiness probe passes, but the readiness probe requires cluster formation, which requires DNS resolution - circular dependency.\nI can break this cycle by either using pod IPs directly in the discovery configuration or enabling `publishNotReadyAddresses` on the headless service to publish DNS records even for unready pods. I'll go with the latter approach and update the service configuration.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3289,"cache_read_input_tokens":35279,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3289},"output_tokens":36,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be64813d-0120-4c22-9f62-37e5510975fc","uuid":"0347bf22-d476-486a-866e-68e73a0cba54","request_id":"req_011CcQRPhdDVkJp5u28pBL9L"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01ATaRqbUWaQ9sGQGhCUELhA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The DNS for pod hostnames only resolves when pods are Ready — a circular dependency. I need to add `publishNotReadyAddresses: true` to the headless service so DNS entries are registered before pods become Ready."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3289,"cache_read_input_tokens":35279,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3289},"output_tokens":36,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be64813d-0120-4c22-9f62-37e5510975fc","uuid":"20d0cbd7-97ad-40b4-8006-effa279f7a9f","request_id":"req_011CcQRPhdDVkJp5u28pBL9L"}
